description: Returns the list of behavior graphs that the calling account is an administrator account of. This operation can only be called by an administrator account. Because an account can currently only be the administrator of one behavior graph within a Region, the results always contain a single behavior graph.

nested_items.name: GraphList
nested_items.description: A list of behavior graphs that the account is an administrator account for.

nested_items.name: Arn
nested_items.description: The ARN of the behavior graph.

nested_items.name: CreatedTime
nested_items.description: The date and time that the behavior graph was created. The value is an ISO8601 formatted string. For example, 2021-08-18T16:35:56.284Z.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: If there are more behavior graphs remaining in the results, then this is the pagination token to use to request the next page of behavior graphs.
